{"tid":2206872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[12手足] 市民「一人一信」：你們不孤單","createTime":"2020-09-17T18:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T05:16:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7d331ec2dfa40c0ff4117ff068c6897a0481a172","tid":2206872,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T18:42:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8H-iJlWUazskbNGzzfUxUsQElx0=/802x1153/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/QOVFI5ZRPFHDJFXCJBLUV5BXYA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8H-iJlWUazskbNGzzfUxUsQElx0%3D%2F802x1153%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQOVFI5ZRPFHDJFXCJBLUV5BXYA.jpg&h=9369555b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】12名港人因涉非法越境被扣深圳鹽田看守所已逾三周，家屬委託的律師仍未能接觸當事人，憂心如焚。有民主派人士昨日起在全港多區擺街站發起一人一信行動，派發明信片予港人撰寫，將心意寄到看守所聲援12位被扣留港人。大批市民到場支持，在心意卡上寫上如「齊上齊落」等鼓勵字句。有參與市民指，對被送中的12名港人感心痛，雖然未知心意卡最終能否送到他們手上，也要堅持去做。<br />\n<br />\n街站昨晚6時開始擺放，不少市民紛紛來到寫卡，心意卡上留下了一句句鼓勵說話，例如有人勉勵他們要堅持、齊上齊落、煲底見等；有人則表示會繼續為他們禱告，「公義在我們的一方，我們並不害怕。」街站約晚上8時結束，兩個小時內已收到逾200張卡。<br />\n<br />\n從事文職的Lydia下班後路經街站前來寫卡，希望支持12名被送中的香港人。她表示，12人中有一名與她年齡相若的女孩，令她感同身受，「好想同佢講佢唔孤單，佢真係好勇敢。」她坦言對事件感到無力，特別香港家屬所委派的內地律師未能接觸他們，「但我都希望畀佢哋知道香港人一直睇住，呢個世界都一直睇住。」<br />\n<br />\n從事教育界的梁小姐表示，很心痛被送中的12名港人，希望寫卡來表達對他們的支持，「佢哋命運就等同於我哋香港人。」她坦言不知道心意卡最後能否送到他們手上，儘管很多事情也徒勞無功，但也要堅持完成，「我希望有一日可以再見，即使要10年定20年都好。」<br />\n<br />\n市民陳小姐寫下10多張心意卡，她明白心意卡能成功送出的機會很渺茫，惟仍希望藉此向政府施壓，令12名港人能平安。她批評政府冷處理此事，沒有盡力協助他們，促當局交代該12名港人是否真的在內地水域被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/JE3YODGAEVENNDGCJS5EWRT4FQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FJE3YODGAEVENNDGCJS5EWRT4FQ%2F&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=562ab803\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2FJE3YODGAEVENNDGCJS5EWRT4FQ%2F&h=c0b7dd55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/JE3YODGAEVENNDGCJS5EWRT4FQ/</a>"},{"pid":"676e74816f53af4e35fddd1b34e055efdc516cb9","tid":2206872,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T18:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b0b975e8e243af42fb5a51753bc1429083cf21","tid":2206872,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"676e74816f53af4e35fddd1b34e055efdc516cb9","tid":2206872,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T18:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T18:43:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b597973d77dbbb2c4c0982efcdccdd53018a784d","tid":2206872,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99b0b975e8e243af42fb5a51753bc1429083cf21","tid":2206872,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"676e74816f53af4e35fddd1b34e055efdc516cb9","tid":2206872,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T18:43:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T18:43