ji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce9ccea478410e3b27384308d7060e14cd9b653","tid":2206872,"uid":11121,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T19:06:37.000Z","msg":"咁有心不如拎哂全部卡反大陸啦<br />\n成日係到做show,明知人地收唔到"}]}